T1  - Toward a theory of conflict in the franchise system
AU  - Spinelli, Steve
AU  - Birley, Sue
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 11
IS  - 5
SP  - 329
EP  - 342
PY  - 1996
DA  - 1996/09/01/
